"it or that information is public, or the First Party believe - in good faith"
" - that the disclosure of the information is imposed by law or the official "
"authority of any governmental council, regulatory or professional body."
msgstr ""

#. module: qlk_management
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:qlk_management.agreements_report
msgid ""
"The First Party obligates to maintain the confidentiality of the data "
"provided by the Second Party, as well as he also obligates to maintain all "
"documents that he receives from the Second Party and to return them to him "
"upon completion of the work entrusted to him unless he has deposited them in"
" the case file in the court and provided the fee dues to the First Party is "
"paid off, and without prejudice the provision of the Article (6) of this "
"Agreement."
msgstr ""

#. module: qlk_management
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:qlk_management.agreements_report
msgid ""
"The First Party shall have the right to withhold any papers, documents or "
"funds come into his possession from or because of the Second Party until the"
" full agreed fees are paid off in accordance with the provision of the "
"Article (41) of the code of Law Practice no: (23) of year 2006 and its "
"amendments."
msgstr ""

#. module: qlk_management
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:qlk_management.agreements_report
msgid ""
"The First party shall be entitled to the full fees agreed upon in this "
"agreement. Even if the second party waived the power of attorney for the "
"first party before ending the work for which he was entrusted or dismissed "
"him for a reason unrelated to the first party, or if the power of attorney "
"was related to a judicial dispute and this dispute ended through "
"conciliation or because of the dismissal or assignment of the lawsuit."
msgstr ""

